General.Name: Vakif Menkul Kiymet Yatirim Ortakligi AS
General.Description: Vakif Menkul Kiymet Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. engages in the managing of capital market instruments portfolio in Turkey. The company was formerly known as Vakif B Tipi Menkul Kiymetler Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. and changed its name to Vakif Menkul Kiymet Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. in April 2014. The company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
